<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="state-n">state <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /steɪt/    美 /steɪt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>状态；情况</strong></h4>
<p>the mental, emotional or physical condition that sb / sth is in：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a confused <strong>state of mind</strong> 
思绪混乱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Antarctica holds 90% of the world’s ice, and most of its fresh water is in a frozen state.
南极洲拥有世界上90%的冰川，其中大部分的淡水处于结冰状态。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although the company showed no sign of declining, it was generally <strong>in an unhealthy state</strong>.
尽管这家公司没有显现出衰退的迹象，但总体来说处于一种不良状态。</p><footer>2013 山东改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>国家；领土；州：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the southern states of America
美国南部各州</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Imagine that you work for the state office of cultural relics.
假设你在国家文化遗产保护办公室工作。</p><footer>人教② – 1</footer></div>

<h3 id="country-nation-state">辨析 country, nation, state</h3>
<p>三者都含有“国家”的意思。<br />
<strong>country</strong> 侧重指“疆土”。
<strong>nation</strong> 侧重指“人民”、“民族”。
<strong>state</strong> 侧重指“政权”、“政体”。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the member states of the EU
欧盟成员国</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The state provides free education.
政府提供免费教育。</p></div></div>